Description: CARLOS (Web) A web application for electronic medical records
  * Patient registration 
  * Scheduling
  * Prescriptions with renal dosage adjustment
  * Chronic disease management 
  * Antenatal care record with antenatal care planner
  * Disease Registry is provided to support population health analyses
  * Supports importing digital(HL7) lab results
  * Complete electronic charting of all encounters
